"(1) (i) The sky over the coastal horizon near the port city of Mumbai began to tremble with an unnatural rumble just before noon, drawing the attention of a lone observer perched on a rooftop. Zoe, a freelance photographer with a keen eye for atmospheric phenomena, felt the ground vibrate through her boots as dark plumes began to rise in the distance, transforming the usual haze into a choking, ashen veil.\n(2) (i) Witnessing a volcanic eruption so close to on , stood transfixed as the eruption's fury unleashed a torrent of ash and searing gases. The air thickened, turning sunlight into a dull gray glow, and the distant roar of the volcano seemed to echo through the labyrinthine streets of the city, etching the day with terror and awe. Greater Mumbai. June 14, 2025. Zoe Brown. witnessed a volcanic eruption."